          "request": {
            "name": "Vessel Photo",
            "description": {
              "content": "Retrieve the most popular photo of a vessel.</br></br> <b>Notes</b> <ul>\n    <li>The <b>frequency of allowed API calls</b> is specific to your API key and is detailed in your contract as a number of successful calls per time period. For example “2 calls per minute”. </br>Regardless of this agreed limit, each API key is technically restricted to a maximum of 100 total (including successful and unsuccessful) requests per minute to ensure system stability.</li>\n</ul>",
              "type": "text/plain"
            },
            "url": {
              "path": [
                "exportvesselphoto",
                ":api_key"
              ],
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "disabled": false,
                  "key": "vessel_id",
                  "value": "<integer>",
                  "description": "(Required) The Maritime Mobile Service Identity (MMSI) or the IMO number of the vessel </br></br> You can <b>instead</b> use shipid"
